470
1902
00:33:53,700 --> 00:33:56,740
Zase jsi ji naštval?

471
1906
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:58,630
Nemluvte o tom.

472
1910
00:33:58,630 --> 00:34:00,540
Jdu zpátky.

473
1914
00:34:35,750 --> 00:34:38,680
